Tarab-fizaa, alam-rubaa, asar sadaa-e-saaz kaa, Jigar mein aag de
lagaa. Har ik lab pe ho sadaa, na haath rok saaqiyaa; Pilaaye jaa,
pilaaye jaa, pilaaye jaaâ Abhi to main jawaan hoon. -- Hafeez Jalandhari

Meaning (from Shashi Kapoor: The Householder, the Star by Aseem Chhabra) 

Maker of song, sing through the night, Kindle that fire in my
life. Maker of wine, ah, donât take flight; Pour on, pour on, pour onâ
For Iâm still young tonight.